data.description: This immaculate 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is the perfect blend of elegance and comfort, designed to meet the needs of the most discerning homeowner. The spacious open-concept living area is flooded with natural light and features vaulted ceilings, a cozy wood burning stove. A modern gourmet kitchen awaits the culinary enthusiast, complete with solid surface countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient breakfast bar. Four well-appointed bedrooms provide plenty of space for family and guests. A versatile loft area can serve as a home office, reading nook, or playroom. Step outside to your own private sanctuary, with a spacious deck. Walk to indoor pool/gym/recreation building and snow tubing hill. Possible seller financing.  Square Footage is estimated
